verbose_text: A boost in CIII 2 levels was detected when using COX7A2L-KO mitochondrial extracts prepared not only in the presence of digitonin but also in the presence of lauryl maltoside (XREF_FIG), which disrupts SC integrity, indicating that the total amount of assembled CIII 2 is increased.
